com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.helper

Class GenerationHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.helper.GenerationHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassGenerationHelper, InterfaceGenerationHelper

    public class GenerationHelper
extends Object
implements Closeable
    GenerationHelper is an internal class that provides common routines only used by the annotation processors.
    Author:
    Brendan Doherty, Florian Sauter, Stephen Haberman (concept)

      • replaceParameters

        public static String replaceParameters(String target,
                       Object... parameters)
        Replaces each placeholder of this string that matches a parameter index.

        Placeholder format: {int}

        Usage:

        replaceParameters("{0} int myField = {1};", "private", 20);
        Parameters:
        target - the string to be replace.
        parameters - the replacement parameters
        Returns:
        the resulting string.

        For example:

        private int myField = 20;
